726401f-a.title: Queens: Corona Avenue - Alstyne Avenue
726401f-a.text:
Corona Avenue, north side, at Alstyne Avenue, showing the Card
Farmhouse (1860). It was razed in 1925. The house stood in line
of Alstyne Avenue, before the thoroughfare was extended to Corona
Avenue.
View 1: 1922
Views 2,3,4: 1923
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
